# Local-only state directories holding large corpora + per-session scratch.
# .workingdir2/ alone holds the 179 GB KonViD-150k corpus + 37 GB CHUG +
# pipeline scratch; without this ignore the dev-mcp build context balloons
# from <2 GB to ~52 GB on dev hosts that hold the corpora.
